{"tid":1032251,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"\"超悶爛尾\"西藏珠峰青海敦煌重慶遊記","createTime":"2019-02-22T08:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T17:38:18.000Z","uid":81372,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8d794bfdde609d27aeb49277ce4f521652b8b225","tid":1032251,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:29:20.000Z","msg":"大家好 , 今次想同大家分享一個旅程<br />\n可能小弟文寫比較差 , 希望大家唔好太介意<br />\n<br />\n其實呢次旅程係比想像中有小小悶<br />\n如果決定收睇既老友 , 希望唔會悶到你地啦<br />\n<br />\n今次去左13日<br />\n<br />\nDay1 - 西寧市內行<br />\nDay2 - 塔爾寺 , 倒淌河 , 青海湖<br />\nDay3 - 茶卡鹽湖 , 翡翠湖<br />\nDay4 - 柴達木盆地 , 陽關<br />\nDay5 - 敦煌莫高窟 , 鳴沙月牙泉<br />\nDay6 - 張掖七彩丹霞<br />\nDay7 - 回到西寧<br />\nDay8 - 火車去拉薩<br />\nDay9 - 拉薩遊<br />\nDay10 - 拉薩遊<br />\nDay11 - 羊卓雍措<br />\nDay12 - 重慶<br />\nDay13 - 重慶回深圳"},{"pid":"81fef0c3578c3373964e62efe7f2182869addb34","tid":1032251,"uid":81372,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:32:14.000Z","msg":"訂了11點深圳~&gt;西寧既機票<br />\n早一日就返左深圳 , 因為知道自己即將好多日都食唔到廣東野<br />\n所以係金光華桃園嘆個夜茶<br />\n之後就去間骨場過夜<br />\n唔知係咪茶既影響 , 3點幾先訓得著 , 總之就唔飲茶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n旅程既第一日 , 一起身竟然8:30!!<br />\n又要浪費百幾蚊飛的去機場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MGJYPZV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMGJYPZV.jpg&h=7785af50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到機場 , 入曬行李 , 行緊去既入集位既時候<br />\n竟然見到有喜茶<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yndh5yj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyndh5yj.jpg&h=b7208eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買左杯飲 , 等成半個鍾 , 到最後都上到機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKrC5yq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKrC5yq.jpg&h=c9c26bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n垃圾飛機餐<br />\n<br />\n到達機場 , 即刻著返件羽絨 , 得幾度<br />\n二千幾海拔 , 行快小小都氣喘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddeJgFd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FddeJgFd.jpg&h=40819594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BJmb90e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBJmb90e.jpg&h=ee22f5e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場巴士好顥眼 , 唔洗點搵都見到<br />\n<br />\n一落車 , 自己都唔知係邊 , 唔緊要 , 伸一伸手再轉的士<br />\n直到酒店"},{"pid":"9c7680a33bb766b3c1c6a54edf8d0dc9994fbe3e","tid":1032251,"uid":50060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:33:50.000Z","msg":"下 西藏珠峰 敦煌 我都去過 好精彩wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未去過青海留名睇下"},{"pid":"274f7196fdfb7368156cf5b161ef24dfd1baa281","tid":1032251,"uid":81372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMXyDT3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMXyDT3.jpg&h=f8c008f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係房休息一陣 , 突然有人敲門 , 原來係送welcome drink<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6A2VSec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6A2VSec.jpg&h=141b12f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咁凍既天氣 , 仲要高海拔 , 我都只係慢行至商場就算了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fp3FiUj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffp3FiUj.jpg&h=9203ac6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJGSUsF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJGSUsF.jpg&h=8777eba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係王府井百貨內 , 見到有冰糖葫蘆 , 仲要10$內 , 我都買左一支 , 幾好味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LMGvF7P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLMGvF7P.jpg&h=1aedcc24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UF1GNNP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUF1GNNP.jpg&h=58843519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZSne7NQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZSne7NQ.jpg&h=f1d1c981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ec2F3mb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fec2F3mb.jpg&h=94306035&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我都幾肚餓 , 因為飛機餐只係食左條蕉 , 所以忍唔住買左呢啲狗餅食(9$)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後穿過一條&quot;美食街&quot; , 又伸手搭的士返酒店了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AGSVSeN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAGSVSeN.jpg&h=ead88348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚餐食美團外賣 , 38$串燒 , 難食過深圳<br />\n冇計啦 , 新年咩鋪都冇開 , 粗粗地啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一日完"},{"pid":"89d23080a807b1d7f32538f9f060ce013e50d41a","tid":1032251,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad2733e13aad0c1f30c9bd538630c471f2653e3","tid":1032251,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留名"},{"pid":"16d3fe16ee55b6b47688f8ef3722c124d7b4f8b0","tid":1032251,"uid":32464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  甘肅去咗，完成咗一個目標，雖然都好開心同 enjoy ，但無以前一開始想像中咁正<br />\n<br />\n留名睇西藏段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c58ee4eb09d15054e402d96371aa0106d0caf4e","tid":1032251,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T03:47:45.000Z","msg":"獨遊?<br />\n3日係西藏?點去珠峰?<br />\n<br />\nD1-D7係咪跟大環線拼車??咁既天氣有咩睇? 6-8月係最好<br />\n敦煌其實吹大左,有D悶"},{"pid":"19f3d53d8fa7a41bc58cf70aaf362386d7fec5ef","tid":1032251,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c58ee4eb09d15054e402d96371aa0106d0caf4e","tid":1032251,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T03:47:45.000Z","msg":"獨遊?<br />\n3日係西藏?點去珠峰?<br />\n<br />\nD1-D7係咪跟大環線拼車??咁既天氣有咩睇? 6-8月係最好<br />\n敦煌其實吹大左,有D悶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T03:51:32.000Z","msg":"我一個人<br />\n<br />\n西藏嚴格黎講只玩左一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nD1~D7係大環線拼車<br />\n咁既天氣冇野好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n敦煌又未去到話悶<br />\n但又真係吹大左囉"},{"pid":"de4d8384fa7e24797920291a6948745e57b07f63","tid":1032251,"uid":34709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T03:52:51.000Z","msg":"想去西藏，等睇留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主有冇去到珠峰個base camp？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51e057ae7b35a44bce336ed53c41726ad13106b","tid":1032251,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de4d8384fa7e24797920291a6948745e57b07f63","tid":1032251,"uid":34709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T03:52:51.000Z","msg":"想去西藏，等睇留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主有冇去到珠峰個base camp？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:00:27.000Z","msg":"真果個封左<br />\n而家大陸佬整左個假既賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係成個大本營搬左落下面個絨布寺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都望到珠峰既"},{"pid":"17ddace290344be1c072e37219a971800c1fb398","tid":1032251,"uid":81372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:06:08.000Z","msg":"Day2<br />\n<br />\n我參加左個淘寶6日5夜團<br />\n司機黎到酒店樓下接我<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9A5o7Cz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9A5o7Cz.jpg&h=2f234f33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我一上車就坐後面 , 點知佢叫我坐助手位 , 因為其他都係2+2<br />\n一對情侶+兩個女仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/axmWJa1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaxmWJa1.jpg&h=c8048142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n齊人之後 , 坐幾個鍾車去塔爾寺<br />\n入場費本身60 , 但用美團買只係30$<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4pKQNCS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4pKQNCS.jpg&h=1934ee1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2bT93bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2bT93bd.jpg&h=b8037166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q85DWwk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ85DWwk.jpg&h=1a5004c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入面冇乜特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廢話唔打咁多了<br />\n出黎後 , 司機帶我地食午餐<br />\n係牛肉面 , 一碗冇牛肉既牛肉面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jBc65pV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjBc65pV.jpg&h=a4a68ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今餐司機請客 , 其實我都做個功課 , 聽講個好多司機都會請團友們先食一餐"},{"pid":"f598caaa57dc90814380bde5f2cd6745225d31b4","tid":1032251,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:11:44.000Z","msg":"又開車喇 , 途徑呢個&quot;拉脊山大石柱&quot;<br />\n落車影張相啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wbaDWw9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwbaDWw9.jpg&h=345df339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/80JuiLZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F80JuiLZ.jpg&h=4edb92f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢道海拔已經三千幾 , 氣喘都愈黎愈勁了<br />\n<br />\n再到呢個&quot;日月山&quot; , 司機話夏天先好睇 , 所以又係門口影張相就走了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XxX3ocO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXxX3ocO.jpg&h=9f5bfda8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又到倒淌河景區 , 因為入面乜鳩都唔開 , 所以只收10$入場費<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7iBWJc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7iBWJc6.jpg&h=30ca1b20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d3UQNET.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd3UQNET.jpg&h=a28e9694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yXYmUj2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyXYmUj2.jpg&h=2904b555&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f60b5c69b3aa648c6b15f486a3d6d6b2ced3854a","tid":1032251,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:24:47.000Z","msg":"依加個6日太環線拼車幾$?<br />\n駛唔駛$1300人仔?<br />\n<br />\n師兄係幾多月去? 其實一條友去呢D好撚尷尬,多數人地係情侶, 之後熟返未<br />\n<br />\n同埋淡季住問題唔駛搵外賓啦?之前我跟呢D港澳台要住外賓,搞到司機分二轉車人去住宿地方"},{"pid":"3c12b4b0170b00d8c78dd4156600ba7338740a58","tid":1032251,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f60b5c69b3aa648c6b15f486a3d6d6b2ced3854a","tid":1032251,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:24:47.000Z","msg":"依加個6日太環線拼車幾$?<br />\n駛唔駛$1300人仔?<br />\n<br />\n師兄係幾多月去? 其實一條友去呢D好撚尷尬,多數人地係情侶, 之後熟返未<br />\n<br />\n同埋淡季住問題唔駛搵外賓啦?之前我跟呢D港澳台要住外賓,搞到司機分二轉車人去住宿地方"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"我六日買淘寶團用左1800 , 再加200$要單人房<br />\n<br />\n我前幾日先返到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一條友冇所謂既 , 幫佢地渣下機影相都幾開心既<br />\n其實拼車真係撞手神<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n非常好彩今次呢6日 , 係好好既團友 , 好岩傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83c429169e46da40c2dc12f658207e3945071a2","tid":1032251,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:24:43.000Z","msg":"新興仔係旅遊台老屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前我好似去四川定唔知桂林<br />\n你都有比個意見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n謝謝你呀"},{"pid":"c24f2014941eadebaba46c561f359faf935f118f","tid":1032251,"uid":72034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b047b5b8f46a9bd752754f6aec94f9390b8d57","t